episodes.title: Richmound was occupied by the Queen of Canada cult for 2 Years
episodes.description:
For two years, the Queen of Canada cult terrorized the village of Richmound. For two years, the Sask. Party government took no action.

The village has spent tens of thousands of dollars on legal fees, infrastructure costs, and additional staffing costs after town employees were threatened and resigned from their positions.

The Saskatchewan NDP is calling on the Sask. Party government to immediately approve the mayor’s request for $75,000 in emergency funding to help Richmound recover.
